# 02 - Research Pipeline
# Multi-step research with sequential goals

NAME research-pipeline
INPUT topic
INPUT depth DEFAULT "comprehensive"

GOAL research "Research $topic at a $depth level. Focus on: key facts (3-5), brief history, current state. Limit to 2 web searches max."
GOAL analyze "Analyze the research findings. Identify 2-3 key patterns or insights. Keep analysis concise."
GOAL synthesize "Write a structured report (500-800 words) with clear sections. Save to research-output.md."

RUN pipeline USING research, analyze, synthesize
